# UI Component Guidelines

## Shopify Polaris Components
Use Polaris for all UI: [Shopify Polaris Documentation](https://polaris.shopify.com/)

Common components:
- Page, Card, Layout
- Button, TextField, Select
- Modal, FormLayout
- Text, InlineStack, BlockStack

