- Fulfillment Health

## Help Text Standards (from [docs/design/help_text_localization_audit.md](mdc:docs/design/help_text_localization_audit.md))

✅ **Good Help Text**:
```tsx
<TextField
  label="Total Pieces"
  helpText="Number of pieces in this order for picker payment calculation"
/>
```

❌ **Avoid Generic**:
```tsx
<TextField label="Amount" /> // Missing help text
```

## Accessibility
Always include proper ARIA labels:
```tsx
<div aria-labelledby={headingId}>
  <h2 id={headingId}>Title</h2>
</div>
```

## Error States
Use clear, actionable messages from [app/utils/error-handler.server.ts](mdc:app/utils/error-handler.server.ts):
```tsx
{error.message || "Unable to load data for this tile. Please try refreshing."}
```
